A helicopter has just landed at the new Government House, Ayoba Villa, Ado-Ekiti. The chopper landed at the Government House helipad few minutes past noon. It has been alleged in some quarters the chopper brought cash from a Southsouth governor. People’s Democratic Party (PDP) members have been trooping to the Government House to collect money. They have been entering Government House through the small gate at the old Governor’s Office. A female party member was seen complaining that he was not given his own share of the cash. She said: “They have not been given my own why some have been given twice. “Anyone that collects this money and vote against Eleka shall not live to spend this money.“